cc:Work.dc:title: Abbe-diagramm
cc:Work.dc:description: An Abbe diagram plots the Abbe number against refractive index for a range of different glasses (red dots). Glasses are classified using a letter-number code to reflect their composition and position on the diagram. Data plotted from the Schott Glass catalogue.

rdf:Bag.rdf:li: Abbe diagramme verre indice réfraction dispersion chromatique
